{"title":"平凡岁月（外一首）","authors":["雷霆"],"dates":[{"year":1988,"month":9,"day":22}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"平凡岁月（外一首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雷霆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"非凡的日子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可遇而不可求，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"并不是每天都值得大书特书。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"非凡的日子写到历史书里了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"虽然书里没有记下我的姓名。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"平凡岁月只有自己记得，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"平凡得如家乡饭菜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却令人久久回味，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如诗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"岩壁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"江上岩壁如削"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乔木灌木，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都成了点点青苔。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"许多代画家"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以种种皴法"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"摹写刀砍斧斫处，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"画卷便是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"莫名的回肠荡气。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"或许如同我之看人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总以目光触其骨骼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"若有金石相击之声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"便引为知己。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}